{"title":"iOS学习资源集合","date":"2016-09-24T02:11:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2016年9月24日","L":"2016/09/24","MM-DD":"09-24"},"link":"2016/09/24/iOS-learning-source","tags":["Objective-C","Swift","iOS"],"categories":["iOS基础"],"updated":"2019-08-17T04:00:54.000Z","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\assets\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><p><img src=\"http://img.frankorz.com/57ee03bfdc293.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>总结个人在学习 iOS 的过程中遇到的精品资源，包含书籍、视频、网站等，一切等待我去探索的好物，主要以Swift 3.0为主。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"视频\">视频<a title=\"#视频\" href=\"#视频\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>视频</th>\n<th>简介</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/course/developing-ios-10-apps-swift/id1198467120\" target=\"_blank\">Developing iOS 10 Apps with Swift</a></td>\n<td>斯坦福白胡子老爷爷最新的 iOS10 和 Swift 3.0 课程。创建于 2017年1月24日，预计时长9周。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/course/developing-ios-9-apps-swift/id1104579961\" target=\"_blank\">Developing iOS 9 Apps with Swift</a></td>\n<td>斯坦福白胡子老爷爷的 iOS9 和 Swift 课程，现在 <a href=\"https://github.com/SwiftGGTeam/Developing-iOS-9-Apps-with-Swift\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a> 只翻译到第三节课。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/course/developing-ios-8-apps-swift/id961180099\" target=\"_blank\">Developing iOS 8 Apps with Swift</a></td>\n<td>斯坦福白胡子老爷爷的 iOS8 和 Swift 课程，已经翻译完成 <a href=\"https://github.com/SwiftGGTeam/Developing_iOS_8_Apps_With_Swift\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.swiftv.cn\" target=\"_blank\">SwiftV课堂</a></td>\n<td>国内一个Swift视频学习站</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.pomo.tv\" target=\"_blank\">pomo.tv</a></td>\n<td>国外一个收集关于Mac、iOS 和 Swift视频的网站</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgwNtYvZGv9STGDSx_knjYyzS7XzmpK84\" target=\"_blank\">Principle UI/UX Animation Tutorials</a></td>\n<td>SketchTV 在 Youtube 上录制的 Principle (交互原型设计软件) 视频，Principle 相关<a href=\"http://principleux.com/principle-chinese-document/\" target=\"_blank\">中文文档</a>，<a href=\"http://principleformac.com/tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\">官方文档</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h3 id=\"youtube-频道\">YouTube 频道<a title=\"#youtube-频道\" href=\"#youtube-频道\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>频道名</th>\n<th>简介</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCysEngjfeIYapEER9K8aikw\" target=\"_blank\">Brian Advent</a></td>\n<td>Follow me around and learn iOS and macOS Development by examples.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-d1NWv5IWtIkfH47ux4dWA\" target=\"_blank\">The Swift Guy</a></td>\n<td>On this channel I put out tutorials, and other types of videos that are relevant to the Swift programming language.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2D6eRvCeMtcF5OGHf1-trw\" target=\"_blank\">CodeWithChris</a></td>\n<td>Learn how to make an app with Swift and Xcode and how to turn your app idea into a reality!</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDIBBmkZIB2hjBsk1hUImdA\" target=\"_blank\">Jared Davidson</a></td>\n<td>IOS Developer / How to Make Apps</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuP2vJ6kRutQBfRmdcI92mA\" target=\"_blank\">Lets Build That App</a></td>\n<td>I’ll do my best to teach you how to build working apps from the AppStore, i.e. YouTube, Facebook, FB Messenger, etc.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChH6WbyYeX0INJjrK2-6WSg\" target=\"_blank\">Mark Moeykens</a></td>\n<td>Free iOS, Xcode and Swift tutorials!</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrhO60YNOqODpMPRQZj2NQg\" target=\"_blank\">Harry Ng</a></td>\n<td>主要是 OSX 的教程</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h3 id=\"书籍\">书籍<a title=\"#书籍\" href=\"#书籍\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>书名</th>\n<th>简介</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://gg.swiftguide.cn\" target=\"_blank\">中文版 Apple 官方 Swift 教程《The Swift Programming Language》</a></td>\n<td>国人发起的官方教程翻译，目前更新到Swift 3.0 <a href=\"https://github.com/numbbbbb/the-swift-programming-language-in-chinese\" target=\"_blank\">Github</a> <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/content/referencelibrary/GettingStarted/DevelopiOSAppsSwift/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">Start Developing iOS Apps (Swift)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.raywenderlich.com/store/ios-10-by-tutorials\" target=\"_blank\">iOS 10 by tutorials</a></td>\n<td>raywenderlich精品书籍，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.appcoda.com/swift/\" target=\"_blank\">Beginning iOS 10 Programming with Swift</a></td>\n<td>appcoda精品书籍，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.appcoda.com.tw/books/\" target=\"_blank\">iOS 10 App 程式設計實力超進化實戰攻略</a></td>\n<td>和楼上电子书对应的湾湾翻译版</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.bignerdranch.com/we-write/ios-programming/\" target=\"_blank\">iOS Programming: The Big Nerd Ranch Guide 5th Edition</a></td>\n<td>The Big Nerd Ranch Guide 推崇困难式学习，该系列书的第四版中译获得豆瓣9.0的高分，目前第六版更新到iOS 10和Swift 3.0，十分值得学习，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/core-image-for-swift/id1073029980?mt=13\" target=\"_blank\">Core Image for Swift</a></td>\n<td>学习 Core Image 框架，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://book.douban.com/subject/26919791/\" target=\"_blank\">Beginning iPhone Development with Swift 3 Exploring the iOS SDK</a></td>\n<td>Apress精品书，本系列中译名为精通iOS编程。这版本讲iOS 10和Swift 3.0，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.gitbook.com/book/zsisme/ios-/details\" target=\"_blank\">ios核心动画高级技巧</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iOS-Core-Animation-Advanced-Techniques-ebook/dp/B00EHJCORC/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1423192842&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Core+Animation+Advanced+Techniques\" target=\"_blank\">iOS Core Animation: Advanced Techniques</a>中文译本，由 OC 编写</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.gitbook.com/book/zonble/kkbox-ios-dev/details\" target=\"_blank\">KKBOX iOS/Mac OS X 基本開發教材</a></td>\n<td>這份教材是為了 KKBOX iOS/Mac OS X 開發部門的新人訓練所設計，目的是培養 出可以開發、維護 KKBOX 的 iOS 與 Mac OS X 版本，以及我們其他軟體產品的工程師。本书由 OC 编写</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://gumroad.com/l/JnWS\" target=\"_blank\">A GUIDE TO IOS ANIMATION 2.0</a></td>\n<td>一本关于 iOS 动画的独具匠心的交互式电子书，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.hackingwithswift.com\" target=\"_blank\">Hacking With Swift</a></td>\n<td>免费在线 Swift 教程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://designcode.io\" target=\"_blank\">Design+Code</a></td>\n<td>学习 iOS 开发设计最好的书籍，付费</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://designthencode.com\" target=\"_blank\">Design Then Code</a></td>\n<td>学会设计和开发 iOS 应用，付费。<a href=\"https://github.com/Cloudox/Motion-Design-for-iOS\" target=\"_blank\">中文翻译</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h3 id=\"网站\">网站<a title=\"#网站\" href=\"#网站\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>网站名</th>\n<th>简介</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/swift/resources/\" target=\"_blank\">Swift Resources</a></td>\n<td>苹果官方为开发者提供的 Swift 学习资源</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://swift.gg\" target=\"_blank\">SwiftGG</a></td>\n<td>国内走心的Swift翻译组，翻译了很多高质量文章</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://swift.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Swift 官方网站</a></td>\n<td>Swift的开源阶段成果和使用指导</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/apple/swift-evolution\" target=\"_blank\">swift-evolution</a></td>\n<td>Swift改进的最新进度</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.raywenderlich.com\" target=\"_blank\">Ray Wenderlich</a></td>\n<td>专注苹果开发，创造大量有价值的开发资源如文章、视频、播客、书籍等。<a href=\"https://www.raywenderlich.com/category/swift\" target=\"_blank\">Swift文章区</a> <a href=\"https://www.raywenderlich.com/category/ios\" target=\"_blank\">iOS文章区</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.learnswift.tips/\" target=\"_blank\">LearnSwift.tips</a></td>\n<td>国外一个学习Swift资源列表网站</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.objc.io\" target=\"_blank\">objc</a></td>\n<td>objc.io是一个专门为iOS和OS X开发者提供的深入讨论技术的平台,文章含金量很高。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.objccn.io\" target=\"_blank\">objc中国</a></td>\n<td>objc翻译组，<a href=\"https://github.com/objccn/articles\" target=\"_blank\">Github</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.appcoda.com.tw/\" target=\"_blank\">APPCoda 台湾</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.appcoda.com\" target=\"_blank\">APPCoda</a> 中教程的翻译，APPCoda 也是专注苹果开发的网站，有自己的电子书和开发教学文章，<a href=\"http://www.appcoda.com.tw/feed/\" target=\"_blank\">RSS</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://nshipster.cn\" target=\"_blank\">NSHipster翻译</a></td>\n<td>NSHipster 关注被忽略的 Objective-C、Swift 和 Cocoa 特性，这里是NSHipster的翻译组网站</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.cocoachina.com\" target=\"_blank\">CocoChina</a></td>\n<td>国内苹果开发中文社区</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://ios.jobbole.com\" target=\"_blank\">伯乐在线</a></td>\n<td>国内分享iOS和Swift开发的网站</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h3 id=\"各大ios资源合集\">各大iOS资源合集<a title=\"#各大ios资源合集\" href=\"#各大ios资源合集\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Github</th>\n<th>简介</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/insidegui/WWDC\" target=\"_blank\">WWDC</a></td>\n<td>非官方的 WWDC app for macOS</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/Aufree/trip-to-iOS\" target=\"_blank\">trip-to-iOS</a></td>\n<td>6000+star的iOS学习资料整理</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/ipader/SwiftGuide\" target=\"_blank\">SwiftGuide</a></td>\n<td>1W+star的swift语言学习资源指南</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/Tim9Liu9/TimLiu-iOS\" target=\"_blank\">TimLiu-iOS</a></td>\n<td>4000+star的iOS开发常用三方库、插件、知名博客汇总</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/jobbole/awesome-ios-cn\" target=\"_blank\">awesome-ios-cn</a></td>\n<td>1W5+star的 <a href=\"https://github.com/vsouza/awesome-ios\" target=\"_blank\">awesome-ios</a> 中译版</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/matteocrippa/awesome-swift\" target=\"_blank\">awesome-swift</a></td>\n<td>9000+star的Swift资源集合</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/dkhamsing/open-source-ios-apps\" target=\"_blank\">open-source-ios-apps</a></td>\n<td>1W+star的开源iOS应用集合</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/raywenderlich/swift-algorithm-club\" target=\"_blank\">swift-algorithm-club</a></td>\n<td>8000+star的Swift算法和数据结构集合，由raywenderlich创建。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/larrynatalicio/15DaysofAnimationsinSwift\" target=\"_blank\">15DaysofAnimationsinSwift</a></td>\n<td>2000+star学习用swift写动画的项目</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/309549\" target=\"_blank\">iOS 开发学习笔记</a></td>\n<td>OneNote笔记，onepkg格式可在win版导入OneNote，笔记适合刚入门的 iOS 开发或有 C 、 OC 基础的同学。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/tangqiaoboy/iOSBlogCN\" target=\"_blank\">iOSBlogCN</a></td>\n<td>中文 iOS/Mac 开发博客列表</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/Draveness/iOS-Source-Code-Analyze\" target=\"_blank\">iOS-Source-Code-Analyze</a></td>\n<td>深入解析 iOS 开源项目 <a href=\"http://draveness.me\" target=\"_blank\">http://draveness.me</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h3 id=\"相关的教程\">相关的教程<a title=\"#相关的教程\" href=\"#相关的教程\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>名称</th>\n<th>简介</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://pomax.github.io/bezierinfo/\" target=\"_blank\">A Primer on Bézier Curves</a></td>\n<td>关于贝塞尔曲线的教程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/yrq110/some-ios-tutorials-with-swift\" target=\"_blank\">some-ios-tutorials-with-swift</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/yrq110\" target=\"_blank\">yrq110</a> 翻译的一些使用 Swift 的 iOS 教程 <a href=\"https://yrq110.gitbooks.io/some_ios_tutorials_with_swift/content/\" target=\"_blank\">Gitbook</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://t.swift.gg/d/2-rxswift\" target=\"_blank\">RxSwift 系列教程</a></td>\n<td>靛青K 发布的 RxSwift 系列教程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.shinobicontrols.com/blog/ios-10-day-by-day-index\" target=\"_blank\">iOS10 Day-by-Day</a></td>\n<td>一个介绍 iOS 10 API 的系列教程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.shinobicontrols.com/blog/ios9-day-by-day-index\" target=\"_blank\">iOS9 Day-by-Day</a></td>\n<td>一个介绍 iOS 9 API 的系列教程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://andrewmika.gitbooks.io/xcode-server-and-continuous-integration-guide-cn/content/\" target=\"_blank\">《Xcode Server and Continuous Integration Guide》中文版</a></td>\n<td>使用Xcode Server进行持续集成，<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/content/documentation/IDEs/Conceptual/xcode_guide-continuous_integration/#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40013292-CH1-SW1\" target=\"_blank\">About Continuous Integration in Xcode</a>的翻译，<a href=\"https://www.gitbook.com/book/andrewmika/-xcode-server-and-continuous-integration-guide/details\" target=\"_blank\">GitBook地址</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/futurice/ios-good-practices\" target=\"_blank\">ios-good-practices</a></td>\n<td>iOS 开发最佳实践</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/ios/human-interface-guidelines/overview/design-principles/\" target=\"_blank\">iOS Human Interface Guidelines</a></td>\n<td>iOS 人机界面指南，<a href=\"https://github.com/Cloudox/iOS-Human-Interface-Guidelines\" target=\"_blank\">中文翻译</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/raywenderlich/swift-style-guide\" target=\"_blank\">Swift编码规范</a></td>\n<td>来自 Ray Wenderlich 的 Swift 编码规范</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/content/documentation/Xcode/Reference/xcode_markup_formatting_ref/\" targ